Yin swings her whip 1350 units to pull herself to a target or the world;
If the Target is an Enemy, she deals 100/140/180/220/260 <AttackDamageText>(+140%</><img id="ADIconOrange"></><AttackDamageText>)</> physical damage, Slows them by 90% for 0.25s, and generates 4 stacks of Rising Storm.
She then leaps in a direction of her choice.
